  • Uses of CountKernelNeighborhoodBase in org.anchoranalysis.image.voxel.kernel.count

    Subclasses of CountKernelNeighborhoodBase in org.anchoranalysis.image.voxel.kernel.count 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  CountKernelNeighborhood
    For every voxel on the outline, count ALL neighbors that are adjacent, including those lying outside the scene.
    class  CountKernelNeighborhoodIgnoreOutsideScene
    For every voxel on the outline, count ALL neighbors that are adjacent, but ignoring any outside the scene.
    class  CountKernelNeighborhoodMask
    The number of touching-faces of a voxel with a neighbor, so long as the neighbor is part of an object-mask
